ragnarok-installer (01-4) stable; urgency=medium

  * New feature: allow users to install custom sets or deb pkgs.
  * Bug fixes:
    * Fixed a bug that messed up disk creation if Rootpass is also
      present in install.conf.
    * Fixed wrong path for /var/messages in afterinstall.
    * Multiple small fixes.

 -- Ian LeCorbeau <I-LeCorbeau@protonmail.com>  Wed, 09 Oct 2024 14:09:12 -0400

ragnarok-installer (01-3) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix critical error in postinst: only create the _installer
    user if it doesn't already exist.

 -- Ian LeCorbeau <I-LeCorbeau@protonmail.com>  Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:25:36 -0400

ragnarok-installer (01-2) stable; urgency=medium

  * New tools: setlocale, setkb, settz. These can be used during
    chroot-style installs to properly and quickly set up the locale,
    timezone and keymap.

 -- Ian LeCorbeau <I-LeCorbeau@protonmail.com>  Sun, 01 Oct 2024 15:33:32 -0400

ragnarok-installer (01-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Use the '_installer' user for commands that need to
    be run without root privileges.

 -- Ian LeCorbeau <I-LeCorbeau@protonmail.com>  Sun, 29 Sept 2024 11:33:52 -0400
